short_description: metalitest is a laboratory equipment supplier based in birmingham, united kingdom.
long_description: with over 150 years combined industry experience, we have the skills and knowledge to provide solutions for your requirements, with a special focus on sample preparation, image analysis and materials testing. born out of a desire to create a one-stop-shop for all materials inspection, analysis and testing. we have a highly configurable product range offering solutions including impact, tensile, compression, bending, fatigue, static, dynamic and creep testing. our customers span numerous industries including but not limited to: aerospace, automotive, construction, energy, academia, manufacturing, textiles and medical/pharmaceutical. backed by our highly experienced service team we offer service, ukas iso 17025 calibration, repair and upgrade of your testing machines.
